         <h3 class="block-header">
          John
          <span>
           Dizikes
          </span>
         </h3>
         <div class="inner">
          <p>
           <img alt="dzikes_300_horiz.jpg" class="" height="160" src="images/thumbs/dzikes_300_horiz.jpg" width="300"/>
          </p>
          <p>
           <span>
            In Memorium: John Dizikes (1932–2018), legendary UC Santa Cruz teacher, and recipient of the UCSC Alumni Association's Distinguished Teaching Award. Since 2002 Humanities has recognized outstanding faculty with the annual John Dizikes Teaching Award.
           </span>
           <a href="https://news.ucsc.edu/2019/01/dizikes-obituary.html">
            More...
           </a>
          </p>
          <p>
